        }
    ]
}
```

*6.4 Deprecated Environment Detection — flag legacy variables for master URI / CA.*

Detect whether legacy/deprecated environment variables are present for supplying the cluster master URI or certificate authority. The check is true when either deprecated variable holds a non-empty value and false when both are absent or empty. Each environment set prints `deprecated=true` or `deprecated=false`.

**Test Cases:** `rcb_tests/public_test_cases/feature6_env_deprecated.json`

